{"tid":2390220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨回應外資於貿合約上棄用香港法律框架：香港國安法實施以來 香港營商環境更良好","createTime":"2021-02-01T11:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:39:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8acfc2acdba0be42d5bb6890e17cfb94b1f15409","tid":2390220,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"外交部：《香港國安法》實施以來 香港營商環境更良好<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》報道，在亞洲經營的大型國際公司，正考慮將香港從法律合同中排除，擔心內地收緊對香港的政策，影響香港法治。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應時表示，香港是法治社會，法治指數始終在全球名列前茅，《香港國安法》制定實施以來，香港法律制度更加完善，營商環境更加良好，是不可否認的客觀事實。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌又說，中央政府將繼續全力支持香港，鞏固和提升國際金融、航運和貿易中心地位，建設亞太區國際法律及爭議解決服務中心，保持長期繁榮穩定，對香港美好的未來充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573510-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573510-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6380314f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573510-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e58c1c5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573510-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"517772844fdfc1c3af18f458ad025d7e7ab38b3e","tid":2390220,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"對支國企黎講？"},{"pid":"d5aff7c08a47ad7b678dd818ff34d1554854da6c","tid":2390220,"uid":39488,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"要呃人首先要呃埋自己"},{"pid":"357b07ca5322d2ee2f9f2fd5b3a2dec0dbdd8aba","tid":2390220,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"基本法賦予架"},{"pid":"62e37a9170fe8b90f8b8a30f98884647110d9650","tid":2390220,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357b07ca5322d2ee2f9f2fd5b3a2dec0dbdd8aba","tid":2390220,"uid":31215